{"tid":1605042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會：包圍檢控官或構成藐視法庭","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:43:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6e53a6ab779239bd2ca54340d544cb8e8e6a4a","tid":1605042,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"大律師公會發表聲明，指日前有人在退庭後一度包圍一名高級檢控官，行為絕對不能容忍，可能構成藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，上周五高等法院審理一名15歲被告的保釋申請，他被控藏有攻擊性武器。有一群旁聽人士在法院內一度包圍及辱罵負責案件的高級檢控官，最終須由保安人員護送離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會認為行為無合理基礎，絕對不能容忍，亦可能構成藐視法庭，呼籲公眾在任何情況下保持理性克制，尊重刑事司法制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364577&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=02454bcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364577&h=b69b0ec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364577</a>"},{"pid":"3bc78366c05627a26dc36bc346bbaa2ae61cac3f","tid":1605042,"uid":148332,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"法庭影相都藐視法庭,捉左果個姓何既動物未?"},{"pid":"a007d0b3f03acf8f8263f693a8958591a73aedf7","tid":1605042,"uid":2772,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"法庭唔再莊嚴<br />\n何來藐視"},{"pid":"f2bdd196ce2ad0dfc0d3ef016ea031a3a00917ff","tid":1605042,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:13:00.000Z","msg":"和平對住條友講野都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁不滿果日咪請sick leave <br />\nCancel 提堂囉on99"},{"pid":"7d5592cc5ad668f6251cd025ebf9e3ff309e1bc9","tid":1605042,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"攻地鐵同機場都係架, 禁制令呀！<br />\n<br />\n咁又點呢？<br />\n<br />\n你個法庭係咪仲有人尊重呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果無, 你諗吓點解啦！"},{